00:05:06.050 --> 00:05:12.769
good effect it has on us to recognize that this arrangement, the marital arrangement is from Jehovah.

00:05:13.569 --> 00:05:19.009
What a good thing that is it makes it so much more powerful to have success in our marriage. We're

00:05:19.009 --> 00:05:27.009
more determined to honor our marriage arrangement. And there's something else too. The binding power

