of our individual spiritual relationship with Jehovah plays a vital role in our marriage because

00:05:32.689 --> 00:05:41.810
we don't just see our mate. We see Jehovah. This is his arrangement. And we honor Jehovah. We honor

00:05:41.810 --> 00:05:48.290
our word to him before him. Then we're going to work very hard to make a success of our marriage.

