and to genuinely enjoy each other. There's a traditional maxim that says a man

00:06:17.089 --> 00:06:23.170
is as good as his word. Doesn't that tie in well with what we're discussing this morning?

00:06:23.170 --> 00:06:28.529
Jehovah he certainly was faithful to his word. It makes me think of a brother that I know

00:06:29.490 --> 00:06:36.129
he's a contractor and consort him a group of investors got together and they wanted him to

00:06:36.129 --> 00:06:44.050
run their company for them. And so he met with them and he laid it out before them very,

00:06:44.050 --> 00:06:51.410
very straight. He said, look, he said, I live by certain Bible principles. I'm one of Jehovah's

00:06:51.410 --> 00:06:58.850
witnesses. So I want you to know at the outset that I will not take advantage of the client.

00:06:59.649 --> 00:07:07.410
I will not cheat the workers. I will be 100% honest in everything I do. I will not use inferior

00:07:07.410 --> 00:07:13.089
material. I'm going to follow the contract and do exactly as I should do. Now if you can live

00:07:13.089 --> 00:07:20.050
with that I'll take the job. Well they said fine, fine, we want you. That's why we've approached

00:07:20.050 --> 00:07:25.490
you. But a little time went by and a couple of the investors said, you know we can make more money

00:07:25.569 --> 00:07:29.970
though. If you would cut a few corners here and there and the brother then got together with all

