deal harshly or wrongly with the employees, he certainly isn't going to cheat the investors

00:07:54.769 --> 00:07:59.730
so what a beautiful thing. Being a man of one's word and following through it brings

00:07:59.730 --> 00:08:04.850
honor to Jehovah and doesn't it make us happy when we hear experiences like that of brothers who

00:08:04.850 --> 00:08:10.129
are firm and stand up. They're not afraid to stand firm for what they know is right. They're people

00:08:10.129 --> 00:08:19.730
of their word and Jehovah undoubtedly blesses them.
